T1  - Infrastructure privatization and changes in corruption patterns: The roots of public discontent
AU  - Martimort, David
AU  - Straub, Stéphane
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 90
IS  - 1
SP  - 69
EP  - 84
PY  - 2009
DA  - 2009/09/01/
SN  - 0304-3878
